{"id":2927,"date":"2025-06-05T09:44:01","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T02:44:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2927"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:18:38","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:18:38","slug":"cach-cham-soc-da-mun","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/cach-cham-soc-da-mun\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>C\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh th\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng tr\u00ean da nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? M\u1ee5n v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd dai d\u1eb3ng, n\u00ean ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n c\u0169ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n. C\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch th\u00f4i nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-nen-cham-soc-da-mun\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n t\u1eeb li ti, b\u00e9, m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u00eam th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n nang, vi\u00eam t\u1ea5y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, <\/span><b>skincare cho da m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1nh bay c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3810\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3810\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3810\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-1.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3810\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ecb em b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ef1 ti, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ecb em th\u01b0\u1eddng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 che \u0111i n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n. Nh\u01b0ng da m\u1ee5n c\u00e0ng make up c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho da t\u1ec7 \u0111i. Nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi, th\u00e2m m\u1ee5n c\u0169, s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam hay v\u1ebft l\u1ed3i l\u00f5m. Khi\u1ebfn cho m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1m tr\u00ean da. M\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 da l\u1ea1i m\u1ed1c n\u1ec1n, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, k\u00e9m s\u1eafc. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u00e1c reviewer tiktoker hay beauty blogger chia s\u1ebb mu\u1ed1n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eb9p b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 l\u00e0n da m\u1ed9c \u00edt khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t. C\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng t\u1ed1t cho da, tr\u00e1nh b\u00f9ng m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. C\u00f9ng xem ngay c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u1edf ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nam-long-cac-buoc-cham-soc-da-mun-tai-nha\"><\/span><b>N\u1eafm l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">5 b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare cho da m\u1ee5n c\u00e1c n\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm l\u00f2ng. Theo kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\/ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n da kho\u1ebb da xinh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, xem ngay:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3811\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3811\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3811\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-2-3.webp\" alt=\"N\u1eafm l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-2-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-2-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-2-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-2-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3811\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u1eafm l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chu-trong-buoc-lam-sach\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ee5n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, l\u00fac n\u00e0y da g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n kh\u00e1c nhau tr\u00ean da. Lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a n\u00ean l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, ph\u1ee5 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi da m\u1ee5n + da hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i( v\u00ed d\u1ee5 s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n, da m\u1ee5n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m..). B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u GSC \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. C\u00f3 2 lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng khi d\u00f9ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n: Th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n. Lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kho\u1ebb, m\u1ee5n nh\u1eb9. N\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecdc b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0: AHA\/BHA\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n: L\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ea theo toa b\u00e1c s\u0129. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ee5n n\u1eb7ng, qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng b\u00e1c s\u0129 s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 pH th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3812\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3812\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3812\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-3-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3812\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi da \u0111ang m\u1ee5n, n\u00e0ng n\u00ean r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Tr\u00e1nh ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t l\u00ean da. Ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t trong th\u1eddi gian b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n. Ngo\u00e0i ra th\u00ec, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch lu\u00f4n c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng h\u00e0m, c\u1ed5, sau tai!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eeda tay, x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng d\u00f9ng cho m\u1eb7t. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1ee5n m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng cho da.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ho\u1eb7c n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eeda tay di\u1ec7t khu\u1ea9n l\u00ean m\u1eb7t. Ch\u00fang s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1ee5n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"can-bang-lam-diu-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t, da m\u1ee5n d\u1ec5 m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u1ecf da, kh\u00f4 da. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, toner c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da s\u1ebd gi\u00fap n\u00e0ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da. N\u00f3 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c c\u1eb7n b\u1ea9n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. C\u00f3 2 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch 1: s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner cho v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t mi\u1ebfng b\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y trang nh\u1ecf, sau \u0111\u00f3 lau nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 c\u1ed5<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch 2: \u0110\u1ed5 toner v\u00e0o tay, th\u1ea5m nh\u1eb9 l\u00ean m\u1eb7t( v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ch\u00fa \u00fd r\u1eeda tay th\u1eadt s\u1ea1ch)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong <\/span><b>c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare cho da m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng. Th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u01b0a da v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u00e9.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-serumkem-muncham-mun\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng serum\/kem m\u1ee5n\/ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi toner \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5m ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o da, da h\u01a1i \u1ea9m nh\u1eb9. L\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n. Th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng serum m\u1ee5n d\u1ea1ng l\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5m nhanh. B\u00f4i thu\u1ed1c m\u1ee5n sau th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cho c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea5m nhanh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3813\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3813\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3813\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-4-3.webp\" alt=\"S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng serum\/kem m\u1ee5n\/ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-4-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-4-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-4-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-4-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3813\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng serum\/kem m\u1ee5n\/ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam: Serum tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n GSC<\/b><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khoa-am-nhe-nhang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kho\u00e1 \u1ea9m nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ecb em ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng da m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u00ed da. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u00e9, sau b\u01b0\u1edbc serum m\u1ee5n da th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1ecb kh\u00f4 h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, bong tr\u00f3c, \u0111\u1ecf da. Th\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng 2 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y nh\u00e9. N\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u nh\u1eb9, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. Khi m\u00ecnh th\u1eed d\u00f9ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m d\u1ea1ng gel, m\u00ecnh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y da \u00edt b\u1ecb b\u00ed h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cream.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1, th\u00ec d\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n sau b\u01b0\u1edbc kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh k\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-quen-buoc-chong-nang\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u1ee7a <\/span><b>c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng. C\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cho l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi. N\u00ean vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng k\u1ef9 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap da b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3814\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3814\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3814\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-5-3.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho da m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-5-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-5-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-5-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/17-5-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3814\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho da m\u1ee5n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 SPF t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf \u0111i nh\u00e9, PA +++. Ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00eam c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da m\u1ee5n. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu da m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang chu\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean l\u1eafng nghe l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft th\u00eam v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n,<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i GSC \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c h\u1eefu \u00edch nh\u1ea5t!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n. C\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch th\u00f4i nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3815,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[12],"class_list":["post-2927","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh","tag-lam-dep-da"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2927","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2927"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2927\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3972,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2927\/revisions\/3972"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3815"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2927"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2927"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2927"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}